{"tid":90752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譴責川普築牆計畫 教宗：民粹將造成「希特拉」出現","createTime":"2017-01-22T10:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T16:57:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05e4d731f0a4bc72162b51eade21df5d9cc3ee80","tid":90752,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"譴責川普築牆計畫 教宗：民粹將造成「希特拉」出現 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1955316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1955316&d=pZBVOThsalqHuy22W8pBzHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0595d92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1955316&h=495d1a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1955316</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZaCygT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZaCygT.jpg&h=93ae3b90&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2017-01-22 15:00 <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普20日上任，天主教宗方濟各（Pope Francis）今天（22日）針對歐美民粹主義上升，警告有可能造成類似希特勒這樣的獨裁者出現。不過，他暫時不願評論川普。 <br />\n<br />\n教宗方濟各今天接受《西班牙國家報》（El Pais）採訪時提到川普，他譴責川普想用牆壁和鐵絲網阻止外國人的做法，他坦言，現在對川普評論還太早，「我們來看看川普會怎麼做！」 <br />\n<br />\n被問到歐美民粹主義興起，方濟各則警告，此危機會導致恐懼和擔憂，歐洲民粹最明顯例子是1933年的希特勒，「德國人投票希特勒，希特拉沒有竊取權力，選民投票給他，但他毀了他的人民。」 <br />\n<br />\n方濟各表示，德國的例子很經典，當年德國人也想用「圍牆和鐵絲網」自衛，讓其他人不能帶走他們的認同，希特勒給了他們「畸形的認同感」。"},{"pid":"1c8deaf054217f77ec57cd0f7208430946b872b2","tid":90752,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d188d93fcf02720b5ffb93331d49942e09c546e","tid":90752,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:03:09.000Z","msg":"說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2301cd529cd0442199f47e6a3de71d082709d828","tid":90752,"ui